Dacorom International - Heavy Lift Transportation
                            Dacorom International provide full worldwide forwarding and logistics activities, door-to-door operations, using multimodal transports (road, sea, river, air and rail), as well as related services  such as warehousing, handling, distribution, all port operations and customs clearance, etc.
                            
