Onshore
Energy XXI recently acquired additional acreage in the South Louisiana Bayou Carlin Field. Currently two wells have been drilled, successfully completed and are producing from the field in St. Mary’s Parish. Energy XXI holds a 73% working interest in the field.  We have acquired new 3D seismic data over 36,000 acres through a JV, which Energy XXI operates and owns a 50% working interest.
 






